pment-trends/\">Emerging WordPress Trends to Follow in 2022</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"khushbu padalia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14516:\"<p>WordPress is a popular content management system that has evolved over several years. This platform powers <strong>more than 42% of the websites</strong> over the internet.</p>\n<p>As we enter 2022, we look forward to the new key trends that revolutionize the web development industry.</p>\n<p>Since its inception, WordPress has been evolving and it offers <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/benefits-of-wordpress-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">outstanding features</a> to build future-ready websites. Being an open-source CMS, it allows WordPress developers to use readymade themes, plugins, and widgets.</p>\n<p>This is an easy-to-use CMS that helps you stay ahead of your competitors. If you are a web developer or business owner looking for custom website development services, you can choose WordPress to build an easy-to-use website at affordable prices.</p>\n<p>Ready to dive in?</p>\n<h2>Top WordPress Trends for 2022</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>1. Voice Search</h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-1024x607.jpg\" alt=\"Voice Search\" width=\"1024\" height=\"607\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-60087\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-1024x607.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-300x178.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-768x455.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-500x296.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-624x370.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-100x59.jpg 100w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-850x504.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-337x200.jpg 337w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185-450x267.jpg 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/Voice-Search-e1588139420185.jpg 1139w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/voice-search-optimization/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Voice Search</a> has become a popular trend for the eCommerce industry. A lot of smartphone users switch to Voice Search instead of typing the products and services they are looking for. It is important to make your WordPress website voice search-friendly.</p>\n<p>Smart speaker devices such as <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Nest_(smart_speakers)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Google Home</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amazon_Alexa\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Alexa</a>, Apple HomePod, and others have been gaining popularity for the last few years.</p>\n<p>It is important to understand user behavior when building your WordPress website. Step into the shoes of your potential audiences and think of different ways in which you can master the voice search algorithm.</p>\n<p>While writing the product descriptions, you should keep in mind what terms the users may be using while searching for those particular products.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. AR/VR</h4>\n<p>Augmented Reality (AR) and Virtual Reality (VR) are real game-changers in the eCommerce industry. Online shoppers prefer to visualize the items they wish to shop online.</p>\n<p>For example, An eCommerce store that offers virtual trials for apparel would get more sales as it becomes easier for the shoppers to try and buy the products from such stores.</p>\n<p>Furniture brand IKEA uses AR technology to help the users visualize how the furniture looks at their place. Virtual in-store experiences or a completely virtual store will redefine the future of the retail industry.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-1024x482.png\" alt=\"IKEA\" width=\"1024\" height=\"482\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-92746\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-1024x482.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-300x141.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-768x362.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-500x235.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-624x294.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-100x47.png 100w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-850x400.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-350x165.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA-450x212.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/IKEA.png 1429w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>[AR] is the direction that I think is far more interesting and promising — for technology and, really, for humanity. AR is designed to add, enhance the things you do as a human being: Being outside, socializing with other people, shopping, playing, having fun. AR can make all those things better.” <em>— John Hanke</em></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. Chatbots</h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot.png\" alt=\"chatbots\" width=\"1000\" height=\"501\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-42341\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot.png 1000w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-300x150.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-768x385.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-500x251.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-624x313.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-850x426.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-350x175.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Chatbot-450x225.png 450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" /></p>\n<p>Plenty of brands uses chatbots to improve the user experience and solve the customers’ queries faster. Chatbots are a quick and fun way to handle the customers’ queries and offer the right information to the users.</p>\n<p>Chatbots can also be used to help users navigate a website and collect valuable feedback.</p>\n<p>You can contact a leading WordPress development company or even use an online chatbot builder to generate more leads and grow your sales. It becomes easy to set up a chatbot with WordPress and enhance your business sales.</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>Also Read: <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/\">Artificial Intelligence – All Set To Transform The Internet (And WordPress)</a></strong></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>4. Drag and Drop Builders</h4>\n<p>Industry experts believe that drag and drop website builders will continue to appeal to the <strong>startups and small business owners</strong> in 2022 also. One can build a feature-rich eCommerce website <strong>without any coding knowledge</strong> or expertise.</p>\n<p>One can launch the website quickly using drag and drop builders. Such builders provide an option to the users to view how the site would look like. There are a lot of plugins that can be used with WordPress to add the desired functionality to your website.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Use of Videos</h4>\n<p>A lot of business websites use videos to promote their products and services. Videos on websites is not a new thing as it has been a common trend for years.</p>\n<p>This trend will continue to appeal to the audiences and brands would invest in video headers and backgrounds to attract potential audiences. <strong>Graphical illustrations grab the attention</strong> of the users and increase sales.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>6. Minimalistic Designs</h4>\n<p>Minimalistic website designs offer smooth navigation to the users. Using flat graphics and white space provides great usability and this trend will remain popular in 2022 also.</p>\n<p>In another word, Minimalism is a style of designing that focuses on being simple and leaving out any nonessential elements in an object. The design style is kind of a reaction against overly ornate and complicated designs. There are many ways of creating minimalist designs. One of them is reducing the number of colors in the design. So avoid using too many colors in the design; this’ll reduce the complexity of the design. </p>\n<p>You can talk to the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/hire-wordpress-developer/\">WordPress developers</a> you hire to get a clutter-free website with a minimalistic design.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>7. Multipurpose WordPress themes</h4>\n<p>WordPress offers several different types of multi-purpose themes that can be used with essential features to launch an eCommerce website. Business owners can choose to build any type of website matching their exact requirements.</p>\n<p>WordPress offers modern multi-purpose themes that can be customized to suit the exact business needs and preferences of business owners.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>8. One-click demo import</h4>\n<p>As WordPress provides a one-click demo import option, the users can check the demo of the themes with a single click. It helps them save a lot of time and effort before selecting the theme for their <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wordpress-customization/\">WordPress website development</a>.</p>\n<p>These unique features allow you to import all menus, categories, comments, posts, and other elements to customize the theme’s demo content.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>9. Mobile-first websites</h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17.png\" alt=\"Mobile Friendly E commerce Site\" width=\"838\" height=\"505\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-41232\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17.png 838w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-300x181.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-768x463.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-500x301.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-624x376.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-100x60.png 100w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-332x200.png 332w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Ecommece-Best-Practices-17-450x271.png 450w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 838px) 100vw, 838px\" /></p>\n<p>One cannot ignore the importance of mobile-first websites in 2022. With the increasing use of smartphones and tablets, website developers and business owners should focus on creating responsive websites to reach a wider audience.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>10. White space</h4>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-1024x486.png\" alt=\"White space\" width=\"1024\" height=\"486\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-92749\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-1024x486.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-300x143.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-768x365.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-500x238.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-624x296.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-100x48.png 100w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-850x404.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-350x166.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space-450x214.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/White-space.png 1463w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><br />\nWhen it comes to building a WordPress website, using white space can attract the users and engage them too. Adding white space on the home page and all the other pages of the website can add value to the site as it provides an <strong>uncluttered look and feels to your website</strong>.</p>\n<p>White spaces on the web pages have gained tremendous popularity in the last few years and this trend will continue to grow in the coming years. So, what are you waiting for? Create an appealing look for your site that attracts visi